Welcome Page

Welcome to the New Caledonia Costco website come here to learn about prices and get into touch with the staff. We were founded a week after the server was made. We have the most experience with giving costumers good wholesale goods. Some of our products include full sets of any type of armor, raw mining materials as well as ingot materials, and much much more. Stop buy our three locations in New Caledonia (located in Diamond Tower), Upper New Caledonia (Located Right Across Alan's Slot Machines), and lastly the latest location in New Vegas( Located In Fort Cucumber). Come by any time. If you Have any questions ask our CEO Adan, or our founder Connor.
